        "creation_date": 1574858716,
        "body": "<p>You can try <code>layoutView.setTag()/getTag()<\/code> instead of keeping your own variable <code>bool<\/code>. <\/p>\n\n<p>Note that you may need to use a <code>Boolean<\/code> object instead of primitive type, for example:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>layoutView.setTag(new Boolean(true));\n\n// inside on click listener\nif (v.getTag() == true) {\n    // do something\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
